  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The anglerfish's bioluminescent lure — activated by velocity. velCutoffAmt at 1.0 means soft playing produces pure darkness (cutoff 120 Hz), while maximum velocity opens the filter to 270 Hz and lets the bio exciter's brightness pierce through. The lure flashes when the fish strikes. Play pp for stalking, ff for the kill.",
  "tags": [
    "bass",
    "velocity",
    "expressive",
    "predator",
    "dynamic",
    "guru-bin",
